      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 17:28:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税可能刺激利率风险、推高通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/trump-tariffs-interest-rate-risk-and-higher-inflation-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[BMO 资本市场美国利率策略主管 Ian Lyngen 分析了唐纳德·特朗普总统提议的关税的更广泛经济影响，以及这些关税为何可能给美联储带来“混乱”时期。Ian 在彭博电台与 Tom Keene 和 Jess Menton 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/trump-tariffs-interest-rate-risk-and-higher-inflation-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 17:23:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LVMH 销售低迷，富裕购物者仍持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/lvmh-posts-subdued-sales-as-wealthy-shoppers-remain-cautious</link>
      <description><![CDATA[LVMH时装和皮革制品销售额第四季度继续下滑，令奢侈品需求快速复苏的前景堪忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/lvmh-posts-subdued-sales-as-wealthy-shoppers-remain-cautious</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 16:54:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>橡树资本的霍华德·马克斯表示低利率时代不会很快回归</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/oaktree-s-howard-marks-says-don-t-expect-low-rate-era-to-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[橡树资本集团有限责任公司 (Oaktree Capital Group LLC) 联合创始人霍华德·马克斯 (Howard Marks) 表示，在轻松赚钱时代赚得盆满钵满的投资者不应期望同样的策略能够在未来带来如此丰厚的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/oaktree-s-howard-marks-says-don-t-expect-low-rate-era-to-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 16:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷蓝航空股价因前景令人失望和成本上升而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/jetblue-loss-narrower-than-expected-on-revenue-lower-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷蓝航空公司预测未来一年的收入将低于预期，且成本将上升，此后该公司股价出现创纪录的暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/jetblue-loss-narrower-than-expected-on-revenue-lower-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 12:17:27 GMT</pubDate>
